## GET

```url
https://api.beatport/v4/catalog/releases/
```

SUBMIT

A ViewSet Mixin that adds routes for recommendations given one or many items as a reference. Recommendations only apply to items whose item_type_id is present in `publish_beatbot`.`source_item_type_id`.

## Parameters

artist_id (query)

Filter by exact artist ID match. Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
artist_name (query)

Filter by case-insensitive artist name containment. Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
catalog_number (query)

Filter by case-insensitive catalog number exact match. Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
created (query)

Filter by exact, less/greater than equal and range. Supports slice syntax: `date=1970-01-01` (exact) `date=:1971-01-01` (less than equal) `date=1970-01-01:` (greater than equal) `date=1970-01-01:1971-01-01` (range)
current_status (query)

Filter on current_status ID exact match. Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
enabled (query)

Filter by enabled boolean match. * `false` - False * `true` - True
encoded_date (query)

Filter by exact, less/greater than equal and range. Supports slice syntax: `date=1970-01-01` (exact) `date=:1971-01-01` (less than equal) `date=1970-01-01:` (greater than equal) `date=1970-01-01:1971-01-01` (range)
exclusive (query)

Filter by exclusive boolean match. * `false` - False * `true` - True
genre_id (query)

Filter by exact genre ID match. Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
genre_name (query)

Filter by case-insensitive genre exact match. Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
id (query)

Filter by exact ID match. Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
is_available_for_streaming (query)

Filter on streaming available boolean match. * `false` - False * `true` - True
is_explicit (query)

Filter on is_explicit boolean match. * `false` - False * `true` - True
is_hype (query)

Filter on is_hype boolean match. * `false` - False * `true` - True
label_enabled (query)

Filter on enabled boolean match. * `false` - False * `true` - True
label_id (query)

Filter by exact label ID match. Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
label_name (query)

Filter by case-insensitive label name containment. Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
label_name_exact (query)

Filter by case-insensitive label name exact match. Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
name (query)

Filter by case-insensitive name containment. Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
new_release_date (query)

Filter by exact, less/greater than equal and range. Supports slice syntax: `date=1970-01-01` (exact) `date=:1971-01-01` (less than equal) `date=1970-01-01:` (greater than equal) `date=1970-01-01:1971-01-01` (range)
order_by (query)

Order by a field. Choices: publish_date, release_date, label, name, id and status. Use -genre for descending order * `publish_date` - Release Date * `-publish_date` - Release Date (descending) * `label` - Label * `-label` - Label (descending) * `name` - Release Name * `-name` - Release Name (descending) * `id` - Release ID * `-id` - Release ID (descending) * `status` - Release Status * `-status` - Release Status (descending) * `release_date` - Release date * `-release_date` - Release date (descending)
page (query)

A page number within the paginated result set.
per_page (query)

Number of results to return per page.
pre_order_date (query)

Filter by exact, less/greater than equal and range. Supports slice syntax: `date=1970-01-01` (exact) `date=:1971-01-01` (less than equal) `date=1970-01-01:` (greater than equal) `date=1970-01-01:1971-01-01` (range)
publish_date (query)

Filter by exact, less/greater than equal and range. Supports slice syntax: `date=1970-01-01` (exact) `date=:1971-01-01` (less than equal) `date=1970-01-01:` (greater than equal) `date=1970-01-01:1971-01-01` (range)
release_type_id (query)

Filter by exact type ID match. Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
sub_genre_id (query)

Filter by exact sub-genre ID match. Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
supplier_id (query)

Filter by case-insensitive name containment. Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
supplier_name (query)

Filter by case-insensitive name containment. Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
track_id (query)

Filter by exact track ID match. Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
track_name (query)

Filter by case-insensitive track name containment. Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
type (query)

Filter on track type. Either Release, Album or Mix Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
type_id (query)

Filter on release type id Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
upc (query)

Filter by exact ID match. Supports `OR` lookup: `param=value1,value2`
updated (query)

Filter by exact, less/greater than equal and range. Supports slice syntax: `date=1970-01-01` (exact) `date=:1971-01-01` (less than equal) `date=1970-01-01:` (greater than equal) `date=1970-01-01:1971-01-01` (range)


##  Curl

```sh
curl -X GET "https://api.beatport.com/v4/catalog/releases/?artist_name=armin" -H "accept: application/json"
```

